BRISEIDA was hustled along off the pace in the two path but was empty turning into the stretch.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: BUILT DIFFERENT saved ground in midpack, angled three wide near the quarter pole, took over between foes in upper stretch, kicked clear nearing the eighth pole and held safe between rivals late. MAJOR PRYCE stalked the pace in the three path, was shut off in upper stretch and was eased from there.
